import Icon from '../../Atoms/Icon/Icon'


export type alphaCardProps = {
  userName: string
  designation: string
  heading: string
  description: string
}



const AlphaCard: React.FC<alphaCardProps> = (props) => {
  const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
    avatar1: {
      width:'136px',
      height:'136px'
    },
  }))
  
  const classes=useStyles()
 
  return (
    <>
      <Grid container sx={container}>
        <Grid item xs={4} sx={imageBox}>

          <Box sx={avatarBox}>
<Icon imageSrc={avatar} classname={classes.avatar1}></Icon>
          </Box>
          
          <Box sx={nameBox}>
            <TypographyComponent
              text={props.userName}
              variant="caption"
              color="#FFFFFF"
            ></TypographyComponent>
            <TypographyComponent
              variant="caption"
              text={props.designation}
              color="#FFFFFF"
            ></TypographyComponent>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Box sx={inputBox}>{props.heading}</Box>
          <Box sx={inputBox1}>{props.description}</Box>

        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </>
  )
}

export default AlphaCard
